# Plasma Doping Tools (Alternative to Ion Implantation)
semicont-07-wfe-doping-equipment:PlasmaDopingTool a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:label "Plasma Doping Tool" ;
    rdfs:comment "Tool for plasma-based doping without ion implantation" ;
