# Doping Process Types
semicont-07-wfe-doping-equipment:ThermalDopingProcess a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:label "Thermal Doping Process" ;
    rdfs:comment "Doping process using thermal diffusion" ;
    rdfs:subClassOf semicont-shared:ProcessStep ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy semicont-07-wfe-doping-equipment: ;
    dc:source "Public domain semiconductor process knowledge" ;
    dc:rights "Fair use: industry-general thermal doping process concepts" ;
    prov:wasInformedBy "Model synthesis of thermal diffusion processes" ;
